core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:36:18.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9b2eae2a14b8c19c647e28f8f571c522d55411a3","tid":502763,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T06:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1884389dcf2cdf6c107a53427601d508f53da4d","tid":502763,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f8f1562b0749b10a7d616abfbcf783b8c57c10f","tid":502763,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"張德榮個申請理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b473b3f167da20143569569a397e01e5ca88cbc","tid":502763,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢次JR其實好正<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明要幾多比例 但立法會係明顯咁違反左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過法庭未必會受理 受左都唔知點判好<br />\n判佢違法又會即刻改法 又咩法律界黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n改法即係要修憲喎</blockquote><br />\n就係迫到人大釋法(改法)<br />\n寫得越指細 自由越收窄 惡果好快浮現</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌個出聲既人唔屌個政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係。咁嗰時出831框架時咪唔應該出聲？<br />\n<br />\n基本法寫得咁清楚係&rdquo;全體議員&ldquo; 二分一。依家話20人。點釋法都釋唔到二分一呢句。<br />\n<br />\n要件事成立，一定要改基本法。依家班垃圾建制派同上面班人死都唔肯改基本法，就係為左唔俾泛民有理據去話基本法可以改。一旦改得基本法，好多野都可以改。<br />\n<br />\n所以，呢單JR成功入稟，之後有機會成個玩法唔同。"}]}